hxvdsp_linux.c is a native FFI shim (not a hexa compilation target).
Linux has no Accelerate/vDSP; this file replaces each vDSP call with
a scalar+O3 loop that auto-vectorises into AVX2/AVX-512. Same ABI as
the Mac wrapper so hexa @link("libhxvdsp") works on both platforms.

Do not transpile, do not include in the stage0 pipeline. Compiled
only by scripts/build_hxblas_linux.sh.
